WEBVTT

1
00:29:39.222 --> 00:29:42.157 
比我大20岁
20 years older than me.

2
00:29:47.663 --> 00:29:50.131 
你们通信吗?
Do you exchange letters?

3
00:29:50.166 --> 00:29:52.396 
不
No.

4
00:29:52.435 --> 00:29:55.404 
我们眉目传情
Secret glances.

5
00:29:58.174 --> 00:30:00.301 
现在看来是难上加难
It all seems difficult and impossible now,

6
00:30:00.343 --> 00:30:04.780 
但我知道  我们必须学会不靠爱情获得快乐
but I just know that we must learn to be happy without love.

7
00:30:04.814 --> 00:30:07.009 
与爱情无关
And in spite of it.

8
00:30:07.049 --> 00:30:09.176 
不靠爱情获得快乐?
Happy without love?

9
00:30:09.218 --> 00:30:11.550 
是的
Yes.

